      <section id="prizes">
      <h3 class="special"><span class="fa fa-bookmark"></span>&nbsp;Prizes</h3>
      <h4 class="special">What prizes will be distributed on May 17, 2017?</h4>
      <p>Two (2) winners at each Google hosted event will win a brand new Google Home or another prize designated by Google.</p>
      <h4 class="special">When is prize distribution?</h4>
      <p>Prizes will only be distributed to those attending Google I/O Extended events at Google offices in Austin, Boulder, Cambridge, Los Angeles, New York City, Pittsburgh, Seattle, Waterloo, San Francisco and Zurich on May 17 or 18, 2017.  Prize distribution information will be announced at Google hosted events.</p>
      <h4 class="special">How do I claim my prize?</h4>
      <p>You must be in attendance of a Google I/O Extended event at a Google office on May 17 or 18, 2017, and must be present at the time of the "announcement of winners" to receive your prize. Failing to claim your prize in-person will result in the event manager selecting the next eligible winner. Restrictions may apply. If you are a government official, you may only compete in the game in your personal capacity and may be ineligible to receive certain prizes. "Government officials" include any government employee; candidate for public office; and employee of government-owned or government-controlled companies, public international organizations, and political parties.</p>
